5000|$|Internal Audit Reviews : Internal audit {{serves as}} a tool for both <b>the</b> <b>Audit</b> <b>Committee</b> and {{management}} to deep-dive into identified high risk areas for identification of issues and recommendations on their remediation. Internal audit frequently reports to <b>the</b> <b>Audit</b> <b>Committee,</b> and can be either internally or externally staffed.|$|E
